node.text:
Take a moment to envision a young woman who has uncertainty and doubts about who she is. 

She is worried about sharing her voice; she may have even been told she is unworthy and incapable. Maybe you have felt this too, so what would you say to her? What would you like to see from her? 

How can we as a community help shift the way all women think of themselves? How can we start changing our thought patterns and start believing we are capable and worthy? 

The Women Gone Wild summit will be an experience of a lifetime where we connected with about 44 speakers, eight celebrities, three musician groups, and most importantly, that one woman! Wild stories will be shared, and that one woman might even be YOU. 

This is why we want you to join us at the upcoming WGW summit from Sept. 28th - Oct. 1st!

This is the time for you to share and sign the manifesto that we've written for thousands of women that says - "I'M HERE TO SUPPORT WOMEN!" So be part of this summit; come and be wild with us!

Join thousands of women and pledge your wildness by signing the WILD manifesto. 
http://wildmanifesto.com

#beunstoppable and #staywild

node.text:
Meet the very first co-author of the Chicken Soup For The Soul titles Diana von Welanetz

Dreams come true!
It was an absolute honor to interview the very first co-author of the Chicken Soup For The Soul titles @diana.w.wentworth, and I just know you guys are going to LOVE this episode!

Diana has been an international keynote speaker at women's meetings, writers conferences and a certified life coach specializing in reinvention! She teaches women storytelling, how to write their own tribute page, how to showcase their life, how to follow intuition, and now she is currently writing her 11th book, Expect Magic!

In this episode, Diana talks about the fact that there's a lot of magic in the untapped exuberance. Women don't need to know what they want, they just need to know the feeling they are trying to achieve, and once they are clear on that feeling, the rest is magic!

Even in today's episode, you'll see some unexpected law of attraction taking place - And I'm going to keep that a secret surprise for when you're watching the video!

She is a thought leader in spiritual awareness and someone I very much admire. You can find more of her on:
Dianawentworth.com
https://www.insideedge.org/

It is without further ado that I share this episode!

So enjoy, and let us know what you think and how inspired you are feeling!

node.title: Diana Wentworth - The Woman Who Brought More Soul To The Chicken Soup

node.text:
Alright everybody, here it is. This is how I'm feeling; a little bit nervous but a whole lot EXCITED for the Women Gone Wild Summit in SEPTEMBER! 

It all seems to be happening so magically fast! Everything is falling into place, and I'm filled with joy to say we hit over 12 number one Best-Selling category and are currently working heavenly on a New York Times Best Seller title! 🤩

Now we are approaching our Women Gone Wild Summit coming up in September! This is going to be one of the craziest things I've ever done! But here's the best part; we are going to streamline a LIVE video call of this event to EVERYONE! 

Our goal is to create a space for 3+ million people to join us online and hear from all the women at the summit, sharing their stories and spreading their voices. 

This is the shift, this is going to be massive! The world needs feminine energy in the marketing system, so SPREAD THE WORD! 💕

I am asking everyone now to show up and support all the women who have stepped forward to share their stories. I am asking everyone to tell their friends and join us for this summit! 

Register here:
Wgwsummit.com

It means the world to all the authors and me! 

THANK YOU! 
#womengonewild @womengonewildbook

node.title: Women Gone Wild Summit coming up in September!

node.text:
What is a USP? Do you have one? 

A USP has many different names, but it boils down to your Unique Selling Proposition; What makes your company stand out, what makes your brand special? How are you differentiating yourself? 

Think about it, what do you do? What is your story? Find that, and double down on that targeted uniqueness, and amplify your message!

So my marketing reminder for the day is - Make sure your USP is always on point. It's the heartbeat of your business! 

#BeUnstoppable #SexyBranding #UnstoppableBrandingAgency

node.text:
Would you like to be one of the next authors in the women gone wild series?! 

This year we have launched the women gone wild book, and after receiving an incredible global response, we've decided to create a series of Women Gone Wild Wealth, Women Gone Wild Relationships, Women Gone Wild Family, Business, Marting; we are trademarking the Women Gone Wild Brand and blowing it up! 

So we want to hear from you; what Women Gone Wild series are you most interested in hearing next, and which book should you be part of? 

We are creating a movement. 

This is your chance to get your story featured in top tier magazines and to sit down for an interview on The Rhonda Swan Show. 

The world has gone feminine, and this is the publication and exposure you deserve. 

It is time for women to go wild! 

I want to meet you!
I want to hear from you! 
And I cannot wait to see you go wild!

Come be wild with us! 

Comment below in the comments what series you want next 🙌🏼

node.title: Are you a woman that has gone wild?

Welcome back to The Rhonda Swan Show! 

We are so excited to see the incredible response we are receiving, and we can't wait for you to receive your book. You guys are going to love it! 

Today, we are interviewing the last three amazing authors of the @womengonewildbook. 

These women are here to share their stories and how you, too, can find your wildness within yourself and take action! 

Without further ado, I am beyond excited to introduce the authors and powerhouse women; @absolutely_alli, @sologirlstravelguide, and @celinnedacosta!

Thank you for following along with the show and sharing this message. The more women who can come together and love each other and share the tools they've used to be wild, the more women we will be able to support on this mission to becoming wild feminine leaders!

Women Gone Wild Digital Book Is Now Live On Amazon Kindle

Come Be Wild With Us!
@womengonewildbook #womensupportingwomen #womenempowerment #womeninbusiness #womenontherise #womenempoweringwomen

node.title: Women Authors Who Challenged The Norms of Society & Went Wild!

node.text:
VAGINA MARKETING

That's right, you heard me!
The marketplace is shifting, and it's something many of us have been talking about for a while. People do not perceive messages the same way they used to. 

We can no longer get away with the traditional approach to writing ad copy that is hard or contrived. Because let's get real, today it is so easy to recognize when we are being sold to.

The way businesses will survive and continue to sell their product is by genuine storytelling, caring about, and having compassion for their audience. 

The Vagina Marketing style is about true connection and leaning into the strengths of the feminine being. It's about finding a new way to market in this new economy. 

This is the shift we need to see; this is how we guide people thoughtfully to our brands. 

Watch the video, and let me know what you guys think! Is this something you would be interested in learning more about? 

Comment below!

node.title: The Feminine Way to Market Your Business & Scale to Infinite Levels.

node.text:
It's been a dream come true to witness the Women Gone Wild book and series bloom into existence over the last year and a half. And here we are, moments away from finally launching! 

This book and project are so important to me. It serves as a roadmap for me to reflect on my experiences and show other women how to break free from their cages and thrive as the lovely feminine beings they are.

One of the important things I've grown to learn is that everyone has an entrepreneur within them.

Entrepreneurship is about being there; it's about being savvy, being able to shift, being resilient, focusing, and making the sacrifice, says Lizzie O'Brien. This book and chapter of my life are about that and working WITH women, not against them.

To meet all the incredible authors, make sure to follow along with the @womengonewildbook!

Get the book at WGWBOOK.com
#womengonewild #booklaunch #womensupportingwomen #womenempowerment #womeninbusiness

node.text:
In Today's episode of The Rhonda Swan Show, we introduce a very special speaker for the Women Gone Wild Summit; Blair Kaplan Venables. 

She has risen from the darkest days with grace and is now sharing her story of resilience to inspire others out there who may be going through similar experiences. 

@blairfromblairland encourages others to be unapologetically themselves, which is how they can start to connect with the wild woman they are.

Blair doesn't make the rules; she breaks them! And in the process, she is inspiring so many, as well as helping herself heal. 

I am so thrilled to have her here today and cannot wait for the summit! 

Get excited, enjoy, and share this inspiring episode! 

Launching SOON! Head to WGWBOOK.com to get on the pre-launch list.

@womengonewildbook #womengonewild #WomenGoneWildBook

node.title: A Story of A Woman Warrior Who Rose From The Darkest Days with Grace

node.text:
This past year, these past few weeks, it's all been a dream come true watching the Women Gone Wild book & series flourish into existence. 

This book and project mean so much to me. It is a roadmap for me to reflect on what I've gone through and to show other women they can break free from their cage and thrive as the beautiful feminine beings they are.

The women and authors in this book are entrepreneurs, leaders, and risk-takers. But I believe entrepreneurship is within all of us. By creating a way of living your life or running your family, you are being an entrepreneur. 

Entrepreneurship is about being there; it's about being savvy, being able to shift, being resilient, focusing, and making the sacrifice. 

In the long run, entrepreneurs know it's going to be worth it. 

This book and chapter of my life are about working WITH women, not against them, building women up, and supporting each other. This is a new journey of women showing up for each other. This is my entrepreneur journey. 

The @womengonewildbook launches August 17th✨🎉
Go to wgwbook.com to get on the pre-launch list 💖

#womengonewild #booklaunch #womensupportingwomen #womenempowerment #womeninbusiness

node.title: The Women Gone Wild Book Launches August 17th!

node.text:
Rhonda here.

And there’s something I’ve been feeling for a while now, deep in my soul, Brian.

Maybe you’re feeling it too?

That a shift is past due.  That change is here.  That our global consciousness is evolving.

And that as women, it’s our time to rise.

To rise from a place of service, confident in our calling to create a better and more conscious world for our children...

To rise into the wildness inside each of us that we’ve buried, held back, and been told to suppress..

To rise into the power we collectively hold to create massive change on every level...

Our time is now.

No more waiting.

No more wishing.

No more wandering alone.

We’re here.  And we need you to join us. 

Because together, we are powerful.

Come be W.I.L.D. with us.
Sign the WILDmanifesto.com 

Rhonda ❤️

#womenleadership #StayWILD #womenempowerment #wildlifeperfection @womengonewildbook @unstoppablefamily @unstoppablesurfer 
@fikrihalim Photo & Styled
@erikapenaofficial dress

node.text:
Take a moment to envision a young woman who has uncertainty and doubts about who she is. 

She is worried about sharing her voice; she may have even been told she is unworthy and incapable. Maybe you have felt this too, so what would you say to her? What would you like to see from her? 

How can we as a community help shift the way all women think of themselves? How can we start changing our thought patterns and start believing we are capable and worthy? 

The Women Gone Wild summit will be an experience of a lifetime where we connected with about 44 speakers, eight celebrities, three musician groups, and most importantly, that one woman! Wild stories will be shared, and that one woman might even be YOU. 

This is why we want you to join us at the upcoming WGW summit from Sept. 28th - Oct. 1st!

This is the time for you to share and sign the manifesto that we've written for thousands of women that says - "I'M HERE TO SUPPORT WOMEN!" So be part of this summit; come and be wild with us!

Join thousands of women and pledge your wildness by signing the WILD manifesto. 
http://wildmanifesto.com

#beunstoppable and #staywild

node.text:
A WILD woman protects herself, her village, and her land. 

She speaks with the truth, grounded in Integrity and Authenticity. She lives and breathes in her highest frequency, receives with complete gratitude, and supports those who are less fortunate. 

She takes a stand for humanity, for freedom, and leads from the heart with grace, she goes first to be the change for generations to come. 

Her willingness to build a business unrestricted by social norms breeds life in her community. Her family endorsed her devotion to solid living leadership and love drives each decision to its obsolete potency, every time. 

Voice is grounded strong unconscious. When you hear her speak her wisdom meets you right where you are, and it moves you. 

She is wild. 
She is you.

Come be wild with us! 
Sign the manifesto: wildmanifesto.com

Written in collaboration by @iam.shannonrose
Film by @dgapone 
Voice & Travel Footage @mashcheb

node.text:
Meet the very first co-author of the Chicken Soup For The Soul titles Diana von Welanetz

Dreams come true!
It was an absolute honor to interview the very first co-author of the Chicken Soup For The Soul titles @diana.w.wentworth, and I just know you guys are going to LOVE this episode!

Diana has been an international keynote speaker at women's meetings, writers conferences and a certified life coach specializing in reinvention! She teaches women storytelling, how to write their own tribute page, how to showcase their life, how to follow intuition, and now she is currently writing her 11th book, Expect Magic!

In this episode, Diana talks about the fact that there's a lot of magic in the untapped exuberance. Women don't need to know what they want, they just need to know the feeling they are trying to achieve, and once they are clear on that feeling, the rest is magic!

Even in today's episode, you'll see some unexpected law of attraction taking place - And I'm going to keep that a secret surprise for when you're watching the video!

She is a thought leader in spiritual awareness and someone I very much admire. You can find more of her on:
Dianawentworth.com
https://www.insideedge.org/

It is without further ado that I share this episode!

So enjoy, and let us know what you think and how inspired you are feeling!

node.text:
Women…Witches

Remember:

"It was not witches who burned.
It was women”

Women who were seen as
Too beautiful
Too outspoken
Had too much water in the well (yes, seriously)
Who had a birthmark
Women who were too skilled with herbal medicine
Too loud
Too quiet
Too much red in her hair
Women who had a strong nature connection
Women who danced
Women who sung
Women who walked proud & or looked confident.

ANY WOMAN WAS AT RISK BURNING IN THE SIXTEEN HUNDREDS

Sisters testified and turned on each other when their babies were held under ice. This is where it started.

Children were tortured to confess their experiences with “witches” & executed in ovens.

Women were held under water and if they float, they were guilty and executed. If they sunk and drowned they were innocent.

Women were thrown off cliffs.
Women were put in deep holes in the ground.

The  start of this madness was years of famine, war between religions and  lots of fear. The churches said that witches, demons and the devil did  exist and women were nothing but trouble. 

Everything connected to a women became feared, especially her  sexuality. It became labeled as dark and dangerous and was the core of  the witch trials through out the world.

Why do I write this?

Because  I think the usage of words are important, especially when we are doing  the work to pull these murky, repressed and forgotten about stories to  the surface. 

Because knowing our history is important when we are  building the new world. When we are doing the healing work of our  lineages and as women. To give the women who were slaughtered a voice,  to give them redress and a chance of peace.

It was not witches who burned.
It was women."

Come Be WILD with us.

~Thank You Fia Forsström
@fikrihalim photo 
@erikapenaofficial dress

Our goal is to create a space for 3+ million people to join us online and hear from all the women at the summit, sharing their stories and spreading their voices.

node.text:
What is a USP? Do you have one? 

A USP has many different names, but it boils down to your Unique Selling Proposition; What makes your company stand out, what makes your brand special? How are you differentiating yourself? 

Think about it, what do you do? What is your story? Find that, and double down on that targeted uniqueness, and amplify your message!

So my marketing reminder for the day is - Make sure your USP is always on point. It's the heartbeat of your business! 

#BeUnstoppable #SexyBranding #UnstoppableBrandingAgency

𝐖𝗼𝗺𝐚𝐧 𝐆𝗼𝐧𝐞 𝐖𝐈𝐋𝐃 𝐌𝐚𝐧𝐢𝐟𝐞𝐬𝐭𝗼

To be a Woman Gone Wild, means to live beyond the conditioning and the constructs of the World we once knew and be the woman who has broken free of the chains that once contained her. 

At a rapid pace, the world is shifting. 

This change has called you into realms of divinely guided leadership and into a Movement of Wild Women, who have linked arms to fearlessly live, fearlessly lead and fearlessly love. 

Where the voice that guides us expands from within. Where head-led living is being replaced with a  devotion to heart-led leadership and pure alignment. 

Every single woman is a Leader. 

You, Queen, are a Leader. Which is why you arrived here. 

Whether you are leading yourself, your family or your community.

Whether you are Single, Married, a Mother, an Entrepreneur, a Healer or a woman with a dream. 

You belong here. 

Feminine leaders have been called to rise and stand front and centre to share their voices and evoke waves of change across our planet.

When a Wild Woman speaks, people listen.

They hear her, they are moved by her and they tell others of her. 

As the World revolutionizes, the foundation of this new construct lies in the strength of Community.  Connection and Courage have already begun to form as the cornerstones of which the pinnacle to our greatest awakening will be built. 

You have been called to be unafraid, to feel deeply, to lean into the nudge that continues to whisper within. 

link arms with us, rise fearlessly. 

BE W.I.L.D. 

We Embrace Wealth...

We Trust Our Intuition...

We Develop Leadership...

We Welcome Diversity...

WE ARE WOMEN GONE WILD!

*COME BE WILD WITH US.*

Tag a WILD WOMAN & SHARE ❤️

🙏 Grateful for the collaberation on this manifesto with @iam.shannonrose
